# Environment Variables

## Google Analytics
# Get your measurement ID from Google Analytics 4 (GA4)
# Format: G-XXXXXXXXXX
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

## AI Content Generation
# Claude API key from Anthropic
# Get from: https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

## Social Media APIs
# Twitter/X API (v2)
TWITTER_BEARER_TOKEN=AAAA...

# LinkedIn API
LINKEDIN_ACCESS_TOKEN=AQV...
LINKEDIN_USER_ID=1234567890

# Instagram Graph API (through Facebook)
INSTAGRAM_BUSINESS_ACCOUNT_ID=123456789
INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN=IGAB...

## Security
# Used to secure API endpoints
API_SECRET_KEY=your-secure-random-key-here

